<div id="review_3852922109" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3852922109" />
    <a title="Homer Smith" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/130837517-homer-smith"><img alt="Homer Smith" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3852922109?book_show_action=true">Feb 21, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Homer Smith" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Homer Smith" href="/user/show/130837517-homer-smith">Homer Smith</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3852922109" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1698613007658206967">Sometimes we all need something a little hot and steamy to read, and J J Sorel is an author I turn to in moments like that. Latest release A Taste of Peace doesn’t disappoint, providing a strong plot, great relationship drama, and strong characters. On top of that the writing is very accomplished and I found myself riveted within the first few pages. I’d recommend for anyone wanting some fun and spicy reading.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


