        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3857198323" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13153609050826338392"><strong>A great start</strong><br/><br/>Although this is a little spicier than I usually read a friend of mine told me to check it out and so I did. The drama that was alluded to it’s going to really start kicking in book to it so I am so glad it’s already out. I love the characters the fast pace dialogue and the real people feel of these billionaire people. I highly recommend this book, If you like a little spice with your romance then you’ll love this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

